| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2769 — Recovery Inhibition (malas)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2a12bfa0-87f3-5684-96b8-fc0f84b8f89a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
